The manual said a good way to make money was to stand outside your town and offer Lay on Hands for Donations.. so I spent an hour or two trying.<br>
<br>
Lower Guk, which I had always thought of as a dangerous place, and I was on-my-toes scared every time I entered.. The first time I entered it on Firiona Vie I was 51 and had the same feeling, until I discovered I could slaughter most of the zone.<br>
<br>
Waiting lists for Orc Hill in the greater Faydark.<br>
<br>
Waiting lists to hunt the Dwarves in Butcherblock. Haven't seen anyone doing that in a long time.<br>
